[p 
	"In this game, RNG doesn't change depending on time. How to manipulate RNG that can be manipulated by Rockman's action without waste time is shown below. You can see its appearance at 0x7E00FB (2byte, hex).
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Hit buster or a part of special weapons to enemy or object.
